open-browser (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Full GTK4 + WebKitGTK4 browser implementation.
  * Built-in ad and tracker blocker.
  * Password manager with libsecret keyring integration.
  * Bookmark and history management.
  * Download manager with pause/resume support.
  * Private browsing mode.
  * Beautiful new tab page with quick-access shortcuts.
  * Full settings UI.

 -- Open Browser Contributors <hello@openbrowser.io>  Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
